summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1644, for the improvement of Florentia Street in the City of Seattle from Westlake Avenue to the east margin of 1st Avenue North by grading the same, under Ordinance No. 17446 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
